RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: select product_group, product_group_description from OLTMS_PRODUCT_GROUP where record_stat = 'O' and auth_stat = 'A'

SELECT DISTINCT P.PRODUCT_CODE, P.PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT P, LBTMS_FACILITY_PRODUCT L, OLTMS_PRODUCT_MASTER_LD B WHERE (L.PRODUCT_CODE = P.PRODUCT_CODE OR B.PRODUCT = P.PRODUCT_CODE) AND P.MODULE = DECODE(?, 'F', 'FC', 'LB') AND P.PRODUCT_TYPE = DECODE(?, 'T', 'C', 'D', 'L', 'F') AND ((((L.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT IS NULL) OR (L.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT = ?)) AND P.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'F') OR (((B.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT IS NULL) OR (B.PARTICIPANT_PRODUCT = ?)) AND P.PRODUCT_TYPE <> 'F'))
SELECT distinct product_code FROM OLTMS_PRODUCT WHERE MODULE = 'LP'
